<h2 id="mla-handbook">MLA Handbook</h2>

<p><strong>What should you ask</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Who is the author of the source?</li>
  <li>Is it a primary source?</li>
  <li>How is this media produced?</li>
  <li>Where did you find this source?</li>
  <li>When was this source published?
