  <li>The Kingdom of Gods (2011)</li>
  <li>The City we Became (2020)</li>
  <li>The Killing Moon (2012)</li>
  <li>The Shadowed Sun</li>
  <li>Clarkesworld Issue 94 (2014)</li>
</ul>

