<h2 id="structure-of-the-profile">Structure of the Profile</h2>

<h3 id="housekeeping">Housekeeping</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Make sure the entire document is Times New Roman 12pt font</li>
  <li>Heading
    <ul>
      <li>On the left margin</li>
      <li>Peer‚Äôs name</li>
      <li>Professor‚Äôs Name</li>
      <li>Date</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="introduction">Introduction</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Hook
    <ul>
      <li>Get the reader interested</li>
      <li>Lighter information</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Who or what is their subject?</li>
  <li>When and where was the subject relavent?</li>
  <li>What makes the subject interesting?</li>
</ul>

