<h2 id="reviews">Reviews</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Find a published review
    <ul>
      <li>Could be either a local or national newspaper</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Essay
    <ul>
      <li>Writing to a more informal audience</li>
      <li>Can be more creative with wording and structure</li>
      <li>You can use personal pronouns</li>
      <li>Worth 30% of overall grade</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Types of reviews
    <ul>
      <li>Media</li>
      <li>Live performances</li>
      <li>Sports</li>
      <li>Greatest or best list</li>
      <li>etc. (See Canvas)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Needs to be at most 2 years old</li>
  <li>First time that our own opinion is apparent in our writing</li>
  <li>We create our own criteria of assessment for the media
